==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Indetermination
<hw>In`de*ter`mi*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>determination</ets>: cf.
<ets>ind⟦eacute⟧termination</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Lack of determination; an unsettled or wavering
state, as of the mind.</def> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Lack of fixed or stated direction.</def>
<rj><au>Abp. Bramhall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indetermined</ent>⟦br⟧
